    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I like to set default values in my models.  This is the method I like to use.</p>

<p>```ruby
  def after_initialize</p>

<pre><code>if new_record?
  self.upper_quantity ||= 0.0
end
</code></pre>

<p>  end
```</p>
